Package com.landawn.abacus.util

Class BiIterator<A,B>

java.lang.Object
com.landawn.abacus.util.BiIterator<A,B>
Type Parameters:
A - the first type of elements returned by this iterator
B - the second type of elements returned by this iterator
All Implemented Interfaces:
Immutable, Iterator<Pair<A,B>>
public abstract class BiIterator<A,B> extends Object
The BiIterator class is an abstract class that extends ImmutableIterator. It represents an iterator over a pair of values of type A and B. This class provides a blueprint for classes that need to implement a bi-directional iterator.
